All Implemented Interfaces:
javax.management.DynamicMBean, javax.management.NotificationBroadcaster, javax.management.NotificationEmitter
public class XhiveFederationMBean
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.management.DynamicMBean, javax.management.NotificationEmitter

A JMX Open MBean to monitor an X-Hive/DB server. Suggestions for extensions to its functionality are invited. Application code is not expected to call any of its methods directly.

Since:
X-Hive/DB 7.0
